{"tid":2110431,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"金牛座tg谷，可能係市面上唯一一個金牛谷","createTime":"2020-07-16T02:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T10:19:02.000Z","uid":217514,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"364e0b46dc78eb21ac434d92c5efd272af33125c","tid":2110431,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"大家好 金牛jj嚟圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我地係有連登post一齊圍爐<br />\n但知道唔係人人想係post到傾/有ac<br />\n所以開多個tg谷 可以入谷圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎曾經入過嘅無限再入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但發現入過嘅係唔會加得返 所以張form都麻煩你備注返<br />\n會有專人另外搵你<br />\n<br />\n歡迎非金牛座嘅人入 一齊為你解決溝金牛仔/女嘅難題<br />\n又或者友情上都可以 唔一定要愛情<br />\n<br />\n請記住 未加前都盡量唔好轉tg id，私隱都較返公開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTg私穩冇較到比任何人加入谷，我係唔會特登Pm你再去加。（你可以係tg設定》私隱同保安〉谷同台》所有人<br />\n<br />\nTg user id:如何設定user id, 設定》編輯個人資料〉用戶名<br />\n<br />\n最後 潛水3日就踢 所以會維持係3日加一次人<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><a href=\"https://forms.gle/tcxcREsGrHU1e1iW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FtcxcREsGrHU1e1iW8&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n38pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=6c0c1175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/tcxcREsGrHU1e1iW8</a></span>"},{"pid":"b14d9b85cb503adbb269f3af96d11dcff972990a","tid":2110431,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db0780c7941fa005734e3f9b603663b67679bcc","tid":2110431,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1922d34c576b4adda6ae929fd679c95d3b2a0ab","tid":2110431,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T07:24:20.000